The hardware device must be connected to either the helm or weapons station.

The 'controls.ini' file in the Artemis directory of the connected station must have the following lines appended to it:
MAIN_SCREEN_FRONT          =           UI_INPUT_KEY_F
MAIN_SCREEN_LEFT           =           UI_INPUT_KEY_L
MAIN_SCREEN_RIGHT          =           UI_INPUT_KEY_R
MAIN_SCREEN_REAR           =           UI_INPUT_KEY_B
MAIN_SCREEN_TACTICAL       =           UI_INPUT_KEY_T
MAIN_SCREEN_SECTOR         =           UI_INPUT_KEY_V
MAIN_SCREEN_STATUS         =           UI_INPUT_KEY_I

Enjoy!
